Class BioStoreHook

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.intermine.bio.dataconversion.BioStoreHook
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataConverterStoreHook

    public class BioStoreHook
extends java.lang.Object
implements DataConverterStoreHook
    An implementation of DataConverterStoreHook that adds DataSet and DataSource references and collections to Items as they are stored.
